拖了后腿。而且我们以后是打算送她出国留学，英语肯定是不能落下。 还有有人说为什么不给弟弟再买一份零食。买也是买过的，但不敢给他买太多，弟弟体质没有他姐好，那些东西吃多了发烧上火，但是他又是那种一有零食就藏不住的那种人，有零食翻箱倒柜也要找到吃完，吃完了我不给买，他又想去拿姐姐零食。幸好现在姐姐上学去了，她的零食都带走了，现在弟弟拿姐姐东西这个情况有所改善。"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ir96x9PKB6upXEAMaCDg0NDU3MTMxIN+Ul5gGMBQ4wwFACXIJNTQ5Nzc5ODA0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"153 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-cf6c6c3a2423a943d379a60c419005e7_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"10_1664935672.9727798","card_id":"Q_557623544","target":{"id":557623544,"title":"如果俄罗斯动用核武器，会不会成为人类公敌？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/557623544","type":"question","created":1664868417,"answer_count":227,"follower_count":291,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[679,5548,42053,167387,167414],"comment_count":9,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"ClUIr96x9PKB6upXEAMaCDg2MTk5MjMyIMHA75kGMAk4owJACnIJNTU3NjIzNTQ0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y","detail_text":"147 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-5899755eeec0412ce72368f5d62f41d3_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1664935672.9733872","card_id":"Q_499046292","target":{"id":499046292,"title":"为什么特斯拉拒绝小鹏前员工应聘?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/499046292","type":"question","created":1636955789,"answer_count":54,"follower_count":152,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[70042,211813],"comment_count":3,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"如题，一直很喜欢特斯拉，但是因为招聘季的gap，不得不先去应聘了小鹏，后来特斯拉恢复招聘后，却说不接受小鹏前员工？"},"attached_info":"ClUIr96x9PKB6upXEAMaCDczMTgwNDk5II3tx4wGMAM4mAFAC3IJNDk5MDQ2MjkyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIA